profile:
Basements & Beyond specializes in Interior Finishing.   We are located in Regina, SK, Canada.  

At Basements & Beyond, our approach is distinctly different.  Our team is experienced, reliable, and thorough.  We provide a variety of services from the initial design consultation and preparation of 2D computerized drawings to custom woodwork, custom built-ins, walk-in closets, tray ceilings, custom bars, wine rooms, fireplaces, entertainment centers, and even home theaters to fit your needs.  We provide interior finishing to basements, kitchens, bathrooms, and apartments.

When you hire Basements & Beyond as your interior finishing contractor, you are guaranteed quality experience, code compliance, detailed proposal packages, and competitive pricing.  Our work speaks for itself.

Please contact us via telephone (306-359-7366) or email (jason@reginacontractors.com).  We will be happy to answer any questions you may have and provide you with an appropriate quote.  Also, feel free to visit our website: http://reginacontractors.com/
